<br>
a) Rotation of LoS-Apex-Triad-IB-Heroes.   <br>
b) VS is slain by the guild up on rotation the day it spawns or it becomes FFA the following day.  <br>
c) Guilds within the rotation may not intermingle to take out VS.  By this they mean Apex can't ask Triad or IB for assistance taking out our Spawn.   If you are part of the rotation, then you must be capable of taking on the spawn.  <br>
<br>
I have no problem with these rules and will abide by them.  So long as there are no objections from the other 3 guilds, I think we have a workable arrangement.<br>
<br>
As an aside, High Level Politics are not alot of fun but they are an important part of trying to maintain harmony on the server.  If you do not have the tact or diplomacy to deal with them, you really are going to cause more problems than you solve.   First lesson you might take to heart, if someone offers the hand of friendship, don't cut it off with a chainsaw. <p>Segal - 60 Cleric - Luclin <br>
